<article id="post-386" class="post-386 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general category-travel tag-british-columbia tag-revelstoke tag-three-valley-gap">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2004/09/bc-vacation-three-valley-gap-calgary/" rel="bookmark">BC Vacation: Three Valley Gap to Calgary</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>No rooster, just the sounds of patrons leaving their rooms. I think I prefered the rooster.<br />
The Chateau&#8217;s name is a little misleading. One is brought to think of the Canadian Pacific (now Fairmont) hotels, with the old world grandeur and luxury. Make no mistake, folks, this ain&#8217;t the Banff Springs. It&#8217;s a 1950&#8217;s motor lodge with a fancy roof. But it&#8217;s comfortable, and the grounds a nicely kitchy. Besides, it&#8217;s a family business, and run very well.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2004/09/bc-vacation-three-valley-gap-calgary/#more-386" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;BC Vacation: Three Valley Gap to Calgary&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2004/09/bc-vacation-three-valley-gap-calgary/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2004-09-08T22:34:21-06:00">8 September 2004</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/travel/" rel="category tag">Travel</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/british-columbia/" rel="tag">british columbia</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/revelstoke/" rel="tag">revelstoke</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/three-valley-gap/" rel="tag">three valley gap</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2004/09/bc-vacation-three-valley-gap-calgary/#respond">Leave a comment<span class="screen-reader-text"> on BC Vacation: Three Valley Gap to Calgary</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
