	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>No-one told me that we were doing any surprises this weekend. &#8216;Course, then it wouldn&#8217;t be a surprise, would it?<br />
Allen (Alex&#8217;s father) took Jean (Alex&#8217;s stepmom) down to Cranbrook so she could catch a flight out to southern Ontario for a wedding. This meant the condo was quiet for a number of hours. That meant we didn&#8217;t get up until late. I love sleeping in.<br />
