<article id="post-374" class="post-374 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general category-travel tag-california tag-conferences tag-san-jose">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2004/08/search-engine-strategies-san-jose-2004-last-day/" rel="bookmark">Search Engine Strategies Conference 2004 San Jose, Last day</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Search Engine Strategies 2004, San Jose, California, Day 4<br />
I should have woken with another hangover. Especially since I had slept only about three hours. It was the last of the seminar, and I didn&#8217;t want to miss anything.<br />
I called Craig&#8217;s room once to see if they were going for breakfast. There was no answer. I wasn&#8217;t surprised.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2004/08/search-engine-strategies-san-jose-2004-last-day/#more-374" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Search Engine Strategies Conference 2004 San Jose, Last day&#8221;</span></a></p>
