	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2004/08/search-engine-strategies-san-jose-2004-last-day/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2004-08-05T22:15:56-06:00">5 August 2004</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/travel/" rel="category tag">Travel</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/california/" rel="tag">california</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/conferences/" rel="tag">conferences</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/san-jose/" rel="tag">san jose</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2004/08/search-engine-strategies-san-jose-2004-last-day/#respond">Leave a comment<span class="screen-reader-text"> on Search Engine Strategies Conference 2004 San Jose, Last day</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
